# CFDataGetTypeID()

**Function**

Returns the type identifier for the CFData opaque type.

## Declaration

```swift
func CFDataGetTypeID() -> CFTypeID
```

## Return Value

The type identifier for the CFData opaque type.

## Discussion

CFMutableData objects have the same type identifier as CFData objects.
